BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.dhs.gov/dhspublic/display%3Fcontent%3D5755"&gt;Four Universities to Collaborate on New Homeland Security Research&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AU.S.%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security"&gt;U.S. Department of Homeland Security&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 25, 2006

</ul>
