BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//dimacs.rutgers.edu/RUHSRI/DHSUniversity.html"&gt;Rutgers/DIMACS named by Department of Homeland Security to coordinate a national research consortium&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ARutgers%20University"&gt;Rutgers University&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 25, 2006

</ul>
