BULLET::::- Brian McGinley. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml%3Fxml%3D/news/2006/07/31/negg31.xml"&gt;The egg that will tell you when it's perfectly boiled&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ATelegraph"&gt;Telegraph&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 31, 2006

</ul>
