BULLET::::- Ian Swanson. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.scotsman.com/international.cfm%3Fid%3D1120252006"&gt;19 die as Israelis stage their deepest attack into Lebanon&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Scotsman"&gt;The Scotsman&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 2, 2006
