BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/5236834.stm"&gt;Israel targets Hezbollah bastion&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News%20Online"&gt;BBC News Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 1, 2006
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20060802/ap_on_re_mi_ea/lebanon_israel"&gt;Israel sends 8,000 troops into Lebanon&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 1, 2006
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2006/WORLD/meast/08/01/mideast.main/index.html"&gt;Israel strikes deep into Lebanon&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 1, 2006

