BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.radionz.co.nz/news/latest/200608031439/33865c2d"&gt;Policeman enters no plea over failed breath test&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ARadio%20New%20Zealand"&gt;Radio New Zealand&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 03, 2006
