BULLET::::- Anne Plummer Flaherty. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.newsvine.com/_news/2006/08/03/310825-generals-raise-fears-of-iraq-civil-war"&gt;Generals Raise Fears of Iraq Civil War&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 3, 2006
BULLET::::- Staff. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/5243042.stm"&gt;US echoes Iraq civil war warning&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News"&gt;BBC News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 3, 2006

</ul>


