BULLET::::- Richard Macey. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.smh.com.au/news/national/one-giant-blunder-for-mankind-how-nasa-lost-moon-pictures/2006/08/04/1154198328978.html"&gt;One giant blunder for mankind: how NASA lost moon pictures&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Sydney%20Morning%20Herald"&gt;The Sydney Morning Herald&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 5, 2006

</ul>
