BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//today.reuters.com/news/articlenews.aspx%3Ftype%3DstageNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D2006-08-07T132217Z_01_L07786316_RTRIDST_0_STAGE-LIFE-BRITAIN-SMOKING-DC.XML"&gt;Churchill's cigar snuffed out at Edinburgh Fringe&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Aug 7, 2006

