BULLET::::- Associated Press. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2006/WORLD/americas/08/05/castro.condition.ap/index.html"&gt;Fidel Castro getting stronger, reports say&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 5, 2006
BULLET::::- Associated Press. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.thestar.com/NASApp/cs/ContentServer%3Fpagename%3Dthestar/Layout/Article_Type1%26amp%3Bc%3DArticle%26amp%3Bpubid%3D968163964505%26amp%3Bcid%3D1154901009132%26amp%3Bcol%3D968705899037%26amp%3Bcall_page%3DTS_News%26amp%3Bcall_pageid%3D968332188492%26amp%3Bcall_pagepath%3DNews/News"&gt;Castro out of bed, says Venezuelan leader&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AToronto%20Star"&gt;Toronto Star&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 6, 2006

