BULLET::::- Joshua Goodman. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/07/AR2006080701197.html"&gt;Colombia's Uribe Begins Second Term&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashington%20Post"&gt;Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 8, 2006

</ul>
