BULLET::::- Sibylla Brodzinsky. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.guardian.co.uk/colombia/story/0%2C%2C1785664%2C00.html"&gt;Bush ally wins in Colombia to halt swing to left in region&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Guardian"&gt;The Guardian&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 30, 2006

