</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- Mark Frauenfelder. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.boingboing.net/2006/08/10/if_the_liquid_could_.html"&gt;If the liquid could be explosive, why are you dumping it in a crowd?&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABoing%20Boing"&gt;Boing Boing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 10, 2006

