BULLET::::- R. Jeffrey Smith. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/07/27/AR2006072701908_pf.html"&gt;Detainee Abuse Charges Feared&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashington%20Post"&gt;Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 28, 2006

</ul>
