BULLET::::- Associated Press. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.latimes.com/news/printedition/asection/la-na-warcrimes10aug10%2C1%2C4466016.story%3Fcoll%3Dla-news-a_section"&gt;Amendments Sought in War Crimes Act&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ALos%20Angeles%20Times"&gt;Los Angeles Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 10, 2006

