BULLET::::- AFP. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cameroon-info.net/cmi_show_news.php%3Fid%3D17903"&gt;Nigeria formally hands over Bakassi to Cameroon&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACameroon-Info.Net"&gt;Cameroon-Info.Net&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 14, 2006
