BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nrel.gov/ncpv/higheff.html"&gt;High-Efficiency Concepts and Concentrators&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANational%20Center%20for%20Photovoltaics"&gt;National Center for Photovoltaics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;,

