BULLET::::- Alok Jha. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.guardian.co.uk/genes/article/0%2C%2C1844803%2C00.html"&gt;Sperm from frozen mice yield healthy offspring&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AGuardian%20Unlimited"&gt;Guardian Unlimited&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 15, 2006
BULLET::::- Mark Henderson. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.timesonline.co.uk/article/0%2C%2C2-2312860%2C00.html"&gt;Mammoths may roam again after 27,000 years&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ATimes%20Online"&gt;Times Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 15, 2006
