BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.canada.com/montrealgazette/news/story.html%3Fid%3D74c47a38-6031-4d62-9d13-7ea9777b1d7c"&gt;1,500 flee chemical cloud&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Montreal%20Gazette"&gt;The Montreal Gazette&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 16, 2006
