BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.newstalkzb.co.nz/newsdetail1.asp%3FstoryID%3D101835"&gt;TV text message competition illegal&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANewstalk%20ZB"&gt;Newstalk ZB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 18, 2006
BULLET::::- NZPA. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.stuff.co.nz/stuff/0%2C2106%2C3767987a12855%2C00.html"&gt;Two men guilty of running illegal texting lottery&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Astuff/NZ%20Lawyer"&gt;stuff/NZ Lawyer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 18, 2006

</ul>
