BULLET::::- Lene Frøslev and Ole Damkjær. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.berlingske.dk/indland/artikel%3Aaid%3D778936%3Afid%3D100101008/"&gt;Storimam genopliver Muhammed-sag&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABerlingske%20Tidende"&gt;Berlingske Tidende&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 18, 2006 . In &lt;a href="w%3ADanish%20language"&gt;Danish&lt;/a&gt;.

