BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/bristol/5266192.stm"&gt;Dead climber found after 17 years&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News%20Online"&gt;BBC News Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 19, 2006

</ul>


